WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:03.337
[♪ pop music playing]

00:45.254 --> 00:48.966
PERFECT CROWN

00:59.851 --> 01:01.019
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

01:01.103 --> 01:02.980
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

01:04.815 --> 01:08.694
[♪ majestic music playing]

01:51.153 --> 01:52.946
[Jeongwoo]
On behalf of the people and the Cabinet,

01:53.530 --> 01:54.865
I offer

01:55.657 --> 01:58.160
my most sincere congratulations
on your union.

01:59.119 --> 02:00.787
[all] Congratulations.

02:01.538 --> 02:05.584
Thank… [coughing]

02:09.004 --> 02:10.172
Seong Huiju.

02:12.090 --> 02:15.052
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

02:16.678 --> 02:17.679
Seong Huiju.

02:27.022 --> 02:29.441
[Huiju breathes heavily]

02:30.734 --> 02:32.569
[guests gasping]

02:34.488 --> 02:35.656
Seong Huiju!

02:35.739 --> 02:37.908
-Huiju.
-Ms. Seong?

02:37.991 --> 02:39.242
Escort His Majesty.

02:39.785 --> 02:40.911
Your Majesty.

02:42.204 --> 02:44.831
-Summon a royal physician!
-[Im] Yes, Your Majesty.

02:44.915 --> 02:46.625
We shall leave the palace.

02:47.125 --> 02:48.377
From this moment forth…

02:49.878 --> 02:54.007
anyone who dares to lay a hand
upon my wife shall face my wrath!

02:54.508 --> 02:55.509
Choi Hyeon!

02:56.885 --> 02:59.304
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness!

03:00.347 --> 03:01.348
Ms. Seong.

03:01.431 --> 03:03.433
-Send word to her father.
-How did this…

03:04.101 --> 03:05.936
-[I-AN] Choi Hyeon!
-Yes, Your Royal Highness!

03:14.403 --> 03:15.529
Huiju.

03:16.113 --> 03:17.114
Seong Huiju.

03:23.120 --> 03:27.040
PERFECT CROWN

03:27.624 --> 03:28.959
EPISODE 8

03:29.668 --> 03:32.212
[reporter] Can you confirm
whether a plan has been established?

03:32.295 --> 03:34.506
Do you care to comment, Ms. Seong?

03:34.589 --> 03:36.758
Can you tell us anything?

03:36.842 --> 03:38.593
Are you all right, Ms. Seong?

03:38.677 --> 03:40.470
Castle Hospital. As fast as you can.

03:41.388 --> 03:42.347
Seong Huiju.

03:42.848 --> 03:44.850
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

03:44.933 --> 03:46.101
[clamoring]

03:49.187 --> 03:51.106
GRAND PRINCESS SEONG
FAINTS MID-WEDDING

03:54.484 --> 03:55.902
Hold on…

04:00.198 --> 04:01.533
Are you all right, sir?

04:01.616 --> 04:03.702
Contact the Ministry of Transport
for traffic control.

04:03.785 --> 04:04.786
Yes, sir.

04:04.870 --> 04:08.707
The escort vehicle must reach
Castle Hospital without any delay.

04:08.790 --> 04:09.791
Understood, sir.

04:10.500 --> 04:11.793
How much of it was broadcast?

04:11.877 --> 04:13.420
It was stopped after her collapse.

04:16.548 --> 04:19.301
Let them know an official statement
will be issued by day's end.

04:19.926 --> 04:22.471
Work with the Royal Guard
on hospital crowd control.

04:22.554 --> 04:23.555
Yes, sir.

04:40.363 --> 04:42.908
[sirens wailing]
STYLE
::cue()

04:47.078 --> 04:50.499
CASTLE HOSPITAL

04:50.582 --> 04:52.000
[doctor] Patient status?

04:52.083 --> 04:55.003
-Looks serious. Let's check her vitals.
-Yes, Doctor.

04:55.629 --> 04:57.005
[doctor] HR 32, BP 80 systolic.

04:57.839 --> 04:59.132
Breathing is weak.

05:00.258 --> 05:02.135
HR in the thirties. Prepare atropine.

05:02.219 --> 05:03.386
[nurse] Yes, Doctor.

05:03.470 --> 05:05.680
[♪ sorrowful music playing]

05:05.764 --> 05:07.557
Please wait outside, Your Royal Highness.

05:09.810 --> 05:11.478
[doctor] Injecting 0.5 ml of atropine.

05:12.854 --> 05:14.481
[nurse] No response to the atropine.

05:14.564 --> 05:16.525
Her pulse is dropping, Doctor.

05:20.570 --> 05:22.072
[breathes heavily]

05:40.090 --> 05:42.259
You're going to the hospital, right?
We'll go too.

05:42.342 --> 05:43.802
No, all of you will stay put.

05:43.885 --> 05:45.720
How can we? Her Ladyship collapsed.

05:45.804 --> 05:46.763
We need to go and--

05:46.847 --> 05:50.392
Everything Ms. Seong consumed
or wore today must be secured.

05:50.892 --> 05:53.019
Don't dispose of anything.
Keep it exactly as is.

05:53.103 --> 05:55.564
What? But why would we do that?

05:55.647 --> 05:57.566
From this moment on,
no one, myself included,

05:58.358 --> 05:59.860
is to leave the private residence.

06:01.987 --> 06:04.322
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

06:24.634 --> 06:25.927
How did this happen?

06:29.347 --> 06:30.515
[doctor] Your Royal Highness.

06:31.892 --> 06:34.227
The blood test results are back.

06:35.186 --> 06:36.771
[sighs]

06:36.855 --> 06:39.274
[machines beeping]

06:39.357 --> 06:40.942
[doctor] She has digoxin toxicity.

06:43.236 --> 06:44.237
Toxicity?

06:45.238 --> 06:47.073
It's medication used to treat arrhythmias,

06:47.157 --> 06:48.283
but an overdose

06:49.367 --> 06:50.869
can be fatal.

06:51.453 --> 06:53.371
What? Fatal?

06:53.455 --> 06:54.539
What does that mean?

06:54.623 --> 06:58.084
Fortunately, we gave emergency treatment
before it hit peak levels in the blood.

06:58.168 --> 07:00.128
She's being treated with an antidote now.

07:00.211 --> 07:02.756
It'll take a few hours
for her to stabilize.

07:02.839 --> 07:05.717
So she's not dying, right?

07:05.800 --> 07:07.594
-Yes.
-[Taeju] You should've started with that!

07:07.677 --> 07:09.304
Gave me a real heart attack there.

07:09.387 --> 07:10.972
Come on, babe. Don't be like that…

07:11.056 --> 07:13.683
They're leaving already?
Shouldn't they explain more?

07:13.767 --> 07:14.768
[Dayeong] Stop it.

07:15.810 --> 07:16.853
[Taeju sighs]

07:19.439 --> 07:21.232
-I was so shocked.
-[Dayeong] Calm down.

07:21.858 --> 07:23.193
-[gasps]
-[Taeju exclaims]

07:23.276 --> 07:24.361
What are you doing?

07:24.444 --> 07:25.737
[I-AN] Stop!

07:28.114 --> 07:29.157
Step back.

07:30.742 --> 07:32.786
[♪ tense music playing]

07:39.167 --> 07:43.088
Surely, you won't just let this slide.

07:44.547 --> 07:45.548
I have…

07:48.718 --> 07:50.470
no intention of letting this slide.

08:06.820 --> 08:08.113
It was due to drug toxicity.

08:08.697 --> 08:09.823
Toxicity?

08:09.906 --> 08:11.032
The attending physician…

08:11.116 --> 08:12.992
Are you saying
someone tried to poison her?

08:17.414 --> 08:19.332
-Where is the Grand Prince right now?
-Sir.

08:19.416 --> 08:21.835
-But now is not…
-Where is Grand Prince I-AN right now?

08:33.471 --> 08:34.597
I knew…

08:37.475 --> 08:39.018
you would fail to protect her.

08:40.311 --> 08:42.147
She collapsed as soon as
she became your wife.

08:42.230 --> 08:44.315
You couldn't even keep her safe for a day!

08:44.399 --> 08:46.484
[breathes heavily]

08:46.568 --> 08:47.777
That's why I'm here.

08:49.070 --> 08:50.071
[scoffs]

08:52.198 --> 08:53.199
Investigate the palace.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.201
What?

08:57.078 --> 08:59.080
From its staff to the royal family.

09:02.333 --> 09:03.501
Investigate them all.

09:05.003 --> 09:07.338
[scoffs]
Do you realize what you're saying--

09:07.422 --> 09:08.465
I do.

09:09.132 --> 09:10.258
So just do it.

09:14.137 --> 09:15.221
Effective immediately…

09:17.849 --> 09:19.392
I hereby authorize a public inquiry…

09:22.687 --> 09:23.772
into the palace.
STYLE
::cue()

09:33.073 --> 09:34.115
You cannot.

09:34.949 --> 09:37.160
The dignity of the Crown will be sullied.

09:37.243 --> 09:38.661
Is that what you seek?

09:40.538 --> 09:42.499
This incident occurred on palace grounds.

09:43.917 --> 09:47.337
This investigation is imperative,
not only for you and His Majesty's safety,

09:47.420 --> 09:48.838
but for the Crown's dignity.

09:48.922 --> 09:51.800
The Royal Protection Branch
can handle that.

09:51.883 --> 09:53.676
An investigation
without privilege is required.

09:56.638 --> 09:57.889
Are you saying…

10:00.058 --> 10:02.143
the royals will be questioned as well?

10:03.269 --> 10:04.646
The Grand Prince authorized it.

10:04.729 --> 10:06.314
I-AN is not the king!

10:06.397 --> 10:07.732
But he serves the Crown…

10:08.483 --> 10:09.734
[♪ tense music playing]

10:11.444 --> 10:12.695
…as its regent.

10:18.034 --> 10:19.327
So, Your Majesty,

10:19.911 --> 10:23.414
please allow the police
to enter the palace.

10:45.019 --> 10:46.396
Before we begin,

10:47.021 --> 10:49.440
we would like to express
our deep concern and regret

10:49.524 --> 10:52.277
over the unfortunate incident
that occurred during the royal wedding.

10:53.570 --> 10:57.157
The Grand Princess was hospitalized
after a medical emergency at the ceremony.

10:57.240 --> 11:00.118
She is presently undergoing treatment
and showing signs of recovery.

11:00.201 --> 11:03.246
You mentioned a medical emergency.
Was there a preexisting condition?

11:03.329 --> 11:05.415
Are external factors being ruled out?

11:07.792 --> 11:10.587
We will take questions
once the statement has concluded.

11:14.382 --> 11:17.427
While the investigation remains ongoing,

11:18.219 --> 11:19.804
concerning factors preclude us

11:20.471 --> 11:22.056
from deeming this a simple accident.

11:25.768 --> 11:29.689
Accordingly, at the Crown's request
and in the interest of the public good,

11:29.772 --> 11:31.316
the government will launch

11:32.025 --> 11:34.152
a public investigation encompassing

11:35.236 --> 11:37.363
the possibility
of intentional harm or terrorism.

11:40.450 --> 11:44.829
The investigation will proceed
with the Ministry of Justice and the NPA,

11:44.913 --> 11:47.457
and will be conducted thoroughly
and transparently.

11:48.708 --> 11:52.295
No political or external pressure
will be permitted to influence

11:53.296 --> 11:54.964
the pursuit of the truth.

11:57.967 --> 11:59.969
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

12:02.055 --> 12:04.057
She didn't eat anything
at the palace that day.

12:04.140 --> 12:07.352
Then, do you remember everything she had
at the private residence?

12:07.435 --> 12:10.313
Uh… She didn't have much of an appetite,

12:10.396 --> 12:12.357
so she only had
half an apple in the morning.

12:13.233 --> 12:15.610
I heard she normally has trouble sleeping.

12:15.693 --> 12:17.403
I wouldn't exactly call it that.

12:17.487 --> 12:18.947
She just doesn't sleep.

12:19.864 --> 12:20.949
She doesn't sleep?

12:21.032 --> 12:23.660
She works through the night in the study.

12:24.244 --> 12:25.495
PERSONAL DETAILS
LEE AREUM

12:25.578 --> 12:28.248
MOTHER: PARK MALJA

12:43.805 --> 12:46.307
[Jeongwoo] No sacred exceptions
in the pursuit of truth.

12:46.808 --> 12:48.226
The palace

12:49.018 --> 12:50.270
will certainly not be exempt.

12:51.229 --> 12:52.355
In the eyes of the law…

12:52.438 --> 12:53.898
Prime Minister Min can be so scary.

12:54.691 --> 12:56.109
It's definitely a bold move.
STYLE
::cue()

12:57.110 --> 12:59.070
Isn't this the first time the Crown

12:59.862 --> 13:01.364
is being investigated?

13:02.156 --> 13:03.241
It is.

13:03.324 --> 13:04.325
What?

13:04.409 --> 13:06.452
Are royals untouchable in investigations?

13:07.537 --> 13:08.913
-Inviolable.
-Right.

13:10.915 --> 13:13.626
Not exactly. It's more like…

13:14.252 --> 13:16.587
But are you two ever going home?

13:17.171 --> 13:19.424
Father told us to stay until she wakes up.

13:19.507 --> 13:20.883
Father is worried…

13:23.219 --> 13:25.221
Wait, I think she moved!

13:25.305 --> 13:26.306
What?

13:30.226 --> 13:33.688
[gasps] Huiju, can you hear me?

13:40.028 --> 13:41.154
[Hyeon] Ms. Seong!

13:41.988 --> 13:43.448
It's me! Hyeon!

13:46.743 --> 13:48.870
-Ms. Seong is awake!
-[sighs]

13:48.953 --> 13:50.455
Thank goodness.

13:52.665 --> 13:54.042
Does His Royal Highness know?

14:09.974 --> 14:11.350
[♪ gentle music playing]

14:19.901 --> 14:22.945
KING HUIJONG THE GREAT
QUEEN UIHYEON

14:25.615 --> 14:26.949
[I-AN] Father…

14:29.285 --> 14:30.870
[whimpering]

14:30.953 --> 14:32.872
How dare you mock

14:32.955 --> 14:35.708
the Crown Prince's authority!

14:40.630 --> 14:42.423
Was I being too greedy again?

14:47.136 --> 14:48.137
Hence…

14:50.348 --> 14:51.682
Is this your wrath,

14:53.434 --> 14:55.019
reminding me not to covet?

14:58.856 --> 15:00.108
How much longer…

15:01.859 --> 15:03.194
Your Royal Highness.

15:04.821 --> 15:07.448
They say she is awake now.

15:10.493 --> 15:12.870
Please slow down,
Your Royal Highness!

15:16.124 --> 15:17.291
Your Royal Highness.

15:17.375 --> 15:18.668
Please slow down.

15:19.252 --> 15:21.129
You will hurt yourself,
Your Royal Highness!

15:44.735 --> 15:45.945
You must be hungry.

15:48.114 --> 15:49.115
Your Royal Highness.
STYLE
::cue()

16:28.362 --> 16:29.614
You're okay, right?

16:41.000 --> 16:42.960
Are you okay now?

16:45.713 --> 16:46.756
Are you crying?

16:53.846 --> 16:55.681
[crying]

17:01.562 --> 17:02.772
I thought you were dying.

17:03.981 --> 17:05.191
I thought I lost you.

17:07.235 --> 17:08.319
I really thought…

17:16.369 --> 17:17.536
[I-AN breathes shakily]

17:28.130 --> 17:29.757
[crying]

17:32.510 --> 17:33.511
I'm okay.

17:40.810 --> 17:42.061
But…

17:42.728 --> 17:44.272
why did I collapse?

17:53.656 --> 17:54.657
[music ends]

17:57.410 --> 17:58.703
[door opens]

18:11.549 --> 18:13.718
This will be a joint investigation
between the NPA

18:13.801 --> 18:15.219
and the Royal Protection Branch.

18:17.888 --> 18:19.056
Today, we are questioning…

18:22.768 --> 18:23.769
It must be me.

18:34.363 --> 18:35.489
You stay here.

18:35.573 --> 18:36.574
Me?

18:39.785 --> 18:40.786
Stay with Seong Huiju.

18:42.246 --> 18:43.247
Never leave her side.

18:48.169 --> 18:49.295
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

18:49.378 --> 18:50.755
Leave everything here to me.

18:57.845 --> 18:58.846
[Huiju] What?

18:59.430 --> 19:00.431
Toxicity?

19:01.182 --> 19:02.183
Me?

19:03.893 --> 19:05.770
I barely even take sleeping aids anymore.

19:07.438 --> 19:09.231
[sighs]

19:10.316 --> 19:14.570
[sighs] Just spit it out already.
Why won't anybody tell me anything?

19:16.697 --> 19:18.324
It looks deliberate.

19:19.492 --> 19:21.243
It's not a medication you normally take.

19:21.911 --> 19:24.038
Even if it were,
the amount found in your system…

19:24.997 --> 19:25.998
Ah.

19:28.584 --> 19:29.710
You don't need to worry.

19:30.294 --> 19:32.254
The investigation is underway,
and the government…

19:32.338 --> 19:33.339
And His Royal Highness?

19:37.218 --> 19:38.761
The medication he usually takes…

19:39.970 --> 19:41.097
Did you check those?
STYLE
::cue()

19:41.180 --> 19:45.810
SEOUL METROPOLITAN POLICE AGENCY

19:51.440 --> 19:53.275
Did Her Royal Highness mention

19:53.359 --> 19:55.486
any abnormal symptoms prior to collapsing?

19:57.154 --> 19:58.155
No.

19:58.239 --> 20:01.075
Any preexisting conditions or allergies?

20:01.158 --> 20:05.246
Did you not review the report
prepared by my wife's attending physician?

20:10.459 --> 20:12.753
Her blood test results

20:13.963 --> 20:15.840
confirmed digoxin toxicity.

20:18.175 --> 20:21.303
By chance,
are you familiar with this medication?

20:21.387 --> 20:24.682
That's not a question
we agreed on beforehand.

20:25.641 --> 20:26.809
I am familiar.

20:27.852 --> 20:28.978
Your Royal Highness.

20:31.647 --> 20:32.648
It is a medication

20:34.567 --> 20:35.985
I have taken on occasion.

20:36.944 --> 20:38.529
Have you checked or not?

20:39.572 --> 20:40.573
Huiju.

20:41.490 --> 20:43.159
[sighing]

20:46.662 --> 20:48.205
I made a mistake.

20:51.709 --> 20:53.753
The robe was so heavy,
and I tripped.

20:55.880 --> 20:57.757
I fell against the table.

20:59.049 --> 21:00.968
Ms. Do put the goblets back in place.

21:01.051 --> 21:02.553
That's when they were switched.

21:03.262 --> 21:04.555
Our goblets.

21:10.186 --> 21:11.312
Where is he right now?

21:15.024 --> 21:16.233
Huiju.

21:16.776 --> 21:18.611
What are you doing? Calm down!

21:18.694 --> 21:20.112
He's in danger right now!

21:22.198 --> 21:23.741
I believe I was the target.

21:25.910 --> 21:27.244
Your Royal Highness.

21:27.328 --> 21:28.746
May I ask why you think that?

21:30.164 --> 21:32.792
My wife, who doesn't normally
take that medication, survived.

21:34.585 --> 21:35.961
However, had I taken it…

21:39.089 --> 21:40.257
I would have died.

21:41.884 --> 21:43.260
It would've been a fatal dose.

21:48.766 --> 21:50.392
Why are you here? What about…

21:50.476 --> 21:51.560
Please go back inside.

21:52.144 --> 21:53.145
No, I need to--

21:53.229 --> 21:55.147
His Royal Highness commanded that

21:55.231 --> 21:56.941
your safety be placed above all else.

21:58.692 --> 21:59.693
Please go back inside.

22:00.903 --> 22:02.154
[Jeongwoo] You stay here.

22:06.826 --> 22:07.952
I will go…

22:09.620 --> 22:10.746
to His Royal Highness.

22:19.046 --> 22:20.339
[sighs]

22:21.632 --> 22:24.134
[♪ piano playing: "Gymnopédie No.1"]

22:55.082 --> 22:56.083
And Grand Prince I-AN?

22:56.584 --> 22:59.628
He is currently giving a statement
with Mr. Jung in attendance.

23:02.965 --> 23:03.883
At this hour?

23:03.966 --> 23:06.719
They've already started
searching his private residence too.

23:07.303 --> 23:09.388
All items used for the wedding,

23:09.471 --> 23:11.432
even the vehicles that transported them,

23:11.932 --> 23:13.809
are said to be subject
to search and seizure.

23:16.520 --> 23:18.606
Take care of any potential issues early.

23:19.148 --> 23:20.441
Make it clean, no loose ends.

23:21.025 --> 23:22.318
Do not worry, Your Majesty.

23:22.401 --> 23:24.236
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

23:37.541 --> 23:38.584
Sir.

23:38.667 --> 23:40.628
These are the personnel files
you asked for.

23:42.254 --> 23:45.799
They include the attendants' family ties,
changes in assets, and their whereabouts

23:45.883 --> 23:47.676
and call history over the past month.

23:48.218 --> 23:49.803
And the Grand Prince's medical records?

23:52.181 --> 23:53.641
Everyone who accessed it recently

23:53.724 --> 23:55.559
are physicians
at the Royal Seoul Hospital.

23:55.643 --> 23:57.019
Less than ten total.

23:57.102 --> 23:59.772
Is Her Majesty's brother one of the ten?

23:59.855 --> 24:01.273
Yes, sir. Both of them.

24:04.193 --> 24:06.987
When will the Royal Seoul Hospital,
including them, be investigated?

24:07.571 --> 24:08.822
Well…

24:08.906 --> 24:09.949
Start now.
STYLE
::cue()

24:12.826 --> 24:13.911
Yes, sir. Understood.

24:17.289 --> 24:18.290
[sighs]

24:21.377 --> 24:22.711
[music ends]

24:30.302 --> 24:32.554
You should head to the palace
when you're done here.

24:33.472 --> 24:34.974
My wife is at the hospital.

24:35.057 --> 24:37.476
[Jeongwoo] When the day breaks,
she will be escorted to the palace.

24:37.559 --> 24:40.062
The palace will be safest for both of you.

24:44.483 --> 24:47.486
It is also the place
where you hold complete control.

24:48.320 --> 24:49.321
I shall handle

24:50.280 --> 24:51.490
all the matters beyond it.

24:52.449 --> 24:54.410
[♪ dramatic music playing]

24:57.538 --> 24:59.623
Your Royal Highness,
are you doing all right?

24:59.707 --> 25:01.834
The Grand Princess shall reside
in Anhwadang Hall.

25:01.917 --> 25:04.378
Pardon? But the private residence is
where she must--

25:04.461 --> 25:06.839
I will also assign new palace attendants.

25:08.090 --> 25:10.300
Royal security will also be reinforced.

25:10.384 --> 25:11.427
Prepare accordingly.

25:11.510 --> 25:12.511
Pardon?

25:15.889 --> 25:17.307
What we need is a fortress.

25:28.068 --> 25:29.862
A CATASTROPHIC DEBUT AT COURT

25:30.529 --> 25:31.655
[Huiju sighs]

25:32.239 --> 25:33.866
Talk about a main character moment.

25:38.746 --> 25:41.290
[sighing]

25:42.166 --> 25:44.001
The sun's up. It's already morning.

25:44.084 --> 25:45.836
-[phone chimes]
-Hmm?

25:45.919 --> 25:48.047
PRINCE:
THE QUESTIONING WENT WELL

25:48.130 --> 25:49.048
PRINCE

25:51.133 --> 25:53.886
-[I-AN] Did you not sleep?
-Where are you? Are you okay?

25:54.803 --> 25:57.264
Wait. Is Jeongwoo there with you?

25:57.890 --> 25:58.891
No, he's not.

25:59.391 --> 26:02.478
I mean, why would you leave
your aide here?

26:02.561 --> 26:04.396
There are plenty of royal guards as it is.

26:05.147 --> 26:06.523
That should be a fun car ride.

26:07.149 --> 26:08.150
What?

26:08.734 --> 26:10.277
Come to the palace. Both of you.

26:14.031 --> 26:18.368
CASTLE HOSPITAL

26:18.452 --> 26:21.080
[♪ tense music playing]

26:31.006 --> 26:32.174
[Dayeong] Huiju.

26:34.134 --> 26:35.385
[sighs]

26:37.971 --> 26:40.516
-Hello, Aide Choi.
-Hello. You're back.

26:40.599 --> 26:42.226
Why are you even back?

26:42.309 --> 26:44.186
I heard you're off to the palace soon.

26:45.687 --> 26:47.815
Is she really okay to be discharged now?

26:47.898 --> 26:51.318
Yes. The detox is complete,
so there shouldn't be any issues.

26:51.401 --> 26:55.030
Still, it would be best to keep her
on ECG monitoring

26:55.114 --> 26:57.407
at the palace for about two more days.

26:57.491 --> 26:58.534
I see. Thank you.

26:58.617 --> 26:59.660
-Thank you, sir.
-Sure.

27:02.162 --> 27:03.872
The palace has been notified, right?

27:04.581 --> 27:06.041
Yes. Anhwadang Hall already has--

27:06.125 --> 27:07.501
[Huiju] Excuse me.

27:08.085 --> 27:09.086
Dayeong.

27:09.711 --> 27:11.421
Father sent me.

27:11.505 --> 27:12.881
[clears throat]

27:13.465 --> 27:16.093
His Royal Highness also asked me for help.

27:18.220 --> 27:19.304
He did?

27:19.388 --> 27:20.931
[♪ whimsical music playing]

27:21.014 --> 27:23.100
Your right-hand woman too.

27:26.478 --> 27:28.730
CASTLE HOSPITAL

27:30.148 --> 27:33.819
Gosh, you look so pretty
even when you're sick.

27:35.904 --> 27:37.948
Do I really look very pretty today too?

27:38.824 --> 27:40.492
Yes. Always very pretty, all the time.

27:41.076 --> 27:42.703
Geez, I can't believe this.

27:42.786 --> 27:44.663
Couldn't my beauty
have taken a break today?

27:45.914 --> 27:47.291
Do you have a cushion on you?

27:47.374 --> 27:48.959
-Cushion?
-This cushion.

27:54.006 --> 27:56.550
[sighs] You weren't lying.

27:57.885 --> 27:58.886
How exhausting.

28:01.388 --> 28:02.848
What are you doing?

28:02.931 --> 28:06.059
The whole country saw me collapse live.

28:06.143 --> 28:08.020
I can't be this pretty
when I'm discharged.

28:08.770 --> 28:10.439
I checked the news early this morning.

28:10.522 --> 28:13.483
Online trolls are spreading some bullshit
about me being a jinx

28:13.567 --> 28:15.527
who brought bad luck
to the palace or whatever.

28:16.862 --> 28:18.071
[inhales sharply] Ah.

28:19.072 --> 28:22.492
The last time Taeju was in hot water,
the sympathy card worked best too.

28:22.576 --> 28:23.577
Let me.

28:25.120 --> 28:26.538
Hmm.

28:27.956 --> 28:29.082
Huiju.

28:29.166 --> 28:31.251
Try putting on a pitiful expression.

28:31.335 --> 28:32.336
Like this.

28:34.212 --> 28:36.131
Why go that far?

28:37.007 --> 28:38.216
[Dayeong] Why not? Just try it.

28:38.300 --> 28:40.469
-You might as well go all out.
-Mm-mmm.
STYLE
::cue()

28:40.552 --> 28:41.929
-There she comes!
-Here she is!

28:42.012 --> 28:44.056
[♪ pop music playing]

28:44.723 --> 28:47.517
The Prime Minister's office suggested
a possible targeted attack.

28:47.601 --> 28:49.728
Can you give us
an update on your condition?

28:49.811 --> 28:52.189
Why were you not treated
at the Royal Seoul Hospital?

28:52.272 --> 28:54.358
-[coughing]
-Hold on. My goodness.

29:03.325 --> 29:04.785
Careful, Your Royal Highness.

29:04.868 --> 29:07.537
[clamoring]

29:17.130 --> 29:19.174
[coughing]

29:23.929 --> 29:24.930
[Hyejeong] All right.

29:25.013 --> 29:27.849
It might feel a bit awkward,
since this isn't our usual approach.

29:27.933 --> 29:30.519
We're going for weak and feeble,
not tough and strong.

29:30.602 --> 29:32.521
But it shouldn't be that difficult.

29:33.021 --> 29:36.358
As the CEO of Castle Beauty,
she was a rich conglomerate heiress.

29:36.441 --> 29:39.444
But at the palace,
she's just a lowborn outcast.

29:39.528 --> 29:40.946
A CATASTROPHIC DEBUT AT COURT

29:41.029 --> 29:43.907
Make her out to be a tragic heroine.

29:43.991 --> 29:45.742
One that you'd totally want to root for.

29:45.826 --> 29:47.160
[passerby 1] What's going on?

29:47.244 --> 29:48.662
VISIBLY GAUNT,
COUGHING CONTINUOUSLY

29:48.745 --> 29:50.330
[passerby 2]
My friend who works at the palace

29:50.414 --> 29:51.790
told me she collapsed there once before.

29:51.873 --> 29:53.208
The Queen Mother is so hard on her.

29:53.291 --> 29:55.335
[passerby 3]
If she didn't marry into the royal family,

29:55.419 --> 29:57.045
she'd be living large as an heiress.

29:57.129 --> 29:58.422
I feel bad for her.

29:58.505 --> 30:00.966
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

30:11.643 --> 30:12.853
[scoffs]

30:16.273 --> 30:17.399
[door opens]

30:22.487 --> 30:23.488
Your Majesty.

30:23.572 --> 30:26.825
The Royal Secretariat submitted
this month's official schedule.

30:29.411 --> 30:31.580
It seems the duties
assigned to the Grand Princess

30:31.663 --> 30:33.040
are being redistributed.

30:33.874 --> 30:37.419
They are wondering how much Your Majesty
is willing to take on in her stead…

30:40.797 --> 30:42.632
Inform them I shall assume all her duties.

30:42.716 --> 30:45.677
Pardon? All of them?

30:47.345 --> 30:49.514
We must present ourselves
as sisters-in-law

30:49.598 --> 30:51.349
in perfect accord.

31:18.668 --> 31:20.378
How shocked you must have been.

31:25.926 --> 31:28.136
I hear you will be staying
at the palace for now.

31:29.387 --> 31:32.057
As it happens,
I have just ordered that all duties

31:32.140 --> 31:34.851
assigned to you be transferred to me.

31:34.935 --> 31:36.978
Just attend to your recovery.

31:37.062 --> 31:40.482
[chuckles] It appears
Her Royal Highness is feeling faint.

31:40.565 --> 31:42.776
[Hyeon] Goodness.
Are you okay, Your Royal Highness?

31:44.069 --> 31:45.821
[♪ tense music playing]

31:45.904 --> 31:47.697
Your Majesty, Her Royal Highness--

31:47.781 --> 31:48.782
I heard.

31:51.076 --> 31:52.327
Please make your way inside.

31:57.457 --> 31:59.751
Forgive me, Your Majesty.
STYLE
::cue()

32:16.852 --> 32:18.145
[♪ melancholy music playing]

32:18.228 --> 32:19.980
[official] The Queen Mother shall lend

32:20.063 --> 32:22.190
her cooperation in preparing

32:22.691 --> 32:25.193
a statement today,
and His Majesty by tomorrow.

32:25.861 --> 32:27.070
However,

32:27.571 --> 32:28.905
Her Majesty has indicated

32:29.948 --> 32:32.200
she will be present
for His Majesty's statement.

32:44.838 --> 32:45.839
The request is denied.

32:47.674 --> 32:48.675
Her Majesty

32:49.342 --> 32:51.803
holds the dignity of the palace above all.

32:52.470 --> 32:54.306
I do not intend to take issue with that.

32:55.348 --> 32:57.767
However, I wish to ease
His Majesty's burden as much as possible.

32:59.686 --> 33:00.937
But His Majesty is--

33:01.021 --> 33:02.522
He should be capable of that much.

33:05.817 --> 33:08.987
He is the sovereign
of a nation, after all.

33:12.824 --> 33:13.825
[door closes]

33:15.952 --> 33:16.953
Your Majesty?

33:17.579 --> 33:18.705
Aunt.

33:21.333 --> 33:23.126
Are you feeling all right?

33:23.710 --> 33:25.795
I heard you were sick.

33:25.879 --> 33:27.505
Ah, were you worried about me?

33:29.132 --> 33:31.426
I heard the police

33:31.509 --> 33:34.846
are coming into the palace
because you fainted.

33:35.972 --> 33:39.768
[chuckles] It is because they are curious.

33:40.352 --> 33:42.270
They want to know
if indigestion was to blame

33:42.354 --> 33:43.980
or if someone pushed me.

33:44.064 --> 33:46.524
No one pushed you.

33:46.608 --> 33:48.902
[chuckles] Yes.

33:48.985 --> 33:51.780
They are investigating
because they want to know those things.

33:53.740 --> 33:55.700
Aide Choi, they are asking you
questions too, right?

33:55.784 --> 33:58.286
Pardon? Yes, of course.

33:58.370 --> 34:01.122
They are asking me. Court Lady Choi too.

34:01.206 --> 34:02.207
You too, right?

34:02.290 --> 34:05.085
Even the street cats
will be questioned, Your Majesty.

34:05.168 --> 34:08.213
Might you be a dummy?

34:08.296 --> 34:09.297
Pardon?

34:09.381 --> 34:11.508
Cats cannot talk.

34:11.591 --> 34:14.636
-[laughs]
-[laughing]

34:19.140 --> 34:21.059
-Your Royal Highness.
-Uncle!

34:28.316 --> 34:29.359
Uncle.

34:32.362 --> 34:33.363
Your Majesty.

34:41.746 --> 34:45.166
[♪ uplifting music playing]

35:12.277 --> 35:14.404
-[gasps]
-[gasps] Ms. Do!

35:14.487 --> 35:15.905
-Hello.
-Wait.

35:16.406 --> 35:18.783
Now, you're Aide Do
of the Grand Prince's office.

35:20.285 --> 35:21.286
Right.

35:22.203 --> 35:23.747
Hello.

35:23.830 --> 35:24.956
Regarding Ms. Seong…

35:27.542 --> 35:28.835
It's just refusing to stick.

35:28.918 --> 35:30.795
[chuckles] I know, right?

35:31.630 --> 35:34.924
Thank you for helping out
with the discharge of Her Royal Highness.

35:35.008 --> 35:37.969
It was nothing. We're family, after all.

35:38.053 --> 35:39.804
Where is Her Royal Highness?

35:41.723 --> 35:42.724
[music ends]
STYLE
::cue()

35:44.225 --> 35:46.895
[I-AN] My wife still does not know
her way around the palace.

35:46.978 --> 35:48.563
She will require the most attentive care.

35:49.064 --> 35:50.815
I will bear that in mind,
Your Royal Highness.

35:51.358 --> 35:55.195
Until new palace attendants are assigned,
the only people permitted in her presence

35:55.278 --> 35:59.282
shall be you, Aide Choi,
Aide Do, and Ms. Han Dayeong.

35:59.366 --> 36:02.327
-Yes, Your Royal Highness.
-Furthermore, my wife

36:02.410 --> 36:04.245
-has trouble sleeping--
-Your Royal Highness.

36:05.622 --> 36:07.207
Yes? Are you feeling unwell?

36:07.791 --> 36:08.792
I'd like…

36:09.876 --> 36:11.544
some alone time with you.

36:14.839 --> 36:16.508
[echoing] Is that not allowed?

36:17.926 --> 36:18.927
[stammers]

36:19.594 --> 36:20.595
No?

36:22.847 --> 36:23.848
Right.

36:24.432 --> 36:25.433
Leave us.

36:26.351 --> 36:27.435
Leave!

36:27.519 --> 36:28.520
Yes, sir.

36:29.479 --> 36:32.273
[♪ light music playing]

36:42.200 --> 36:43.535
We must be understanding.

36:43.618 --> 36:44.994
They are newlyweds, after all.

36:47.330 --> 36:48.331
Newlyweds.

36:49.082 --> 36:50.333
[sighs]

36:50.917 --> 36:52.335
-My goodness.
-[laughs]

36:55.130 --> 36:56.339
[music ends]

37:05.056 --> 37:06.057
[sighs]

37:06.141 --> 37:07.976
Is this why you wanted to be alone?

37:09.561 --> 37:10.895
You know,

37:11.438 --> 37:13.982
I really thought I could remain unfazed
by my new title.

37:16.151 --> 37:18.695
But now that everyone is calling me,
"Your Royal Highness"…

37:21.197 --> 37:22.699
I can't help but be a bit cautious.

37:23.825 --> 37:27.162
It feels like I should be
the epitome of elegance every second.

37:27.954 --> 37:30.999
Everyone is monitoring me,
both at the hospital and here.

37:31.082 --> 37:32.417
Not monitoring. Protecting.

37:37.672 --> 37:40.216
And the questioning? Did it go well?

37:41.968 --> 37:44.220
[sighs] Well… I almost fell asleep.

37:45.680 --> 37:46.681
But it was fine.

37:51.811 --> 37:55.440
Listen, I've been thinking about it…

37:57.734 --> 38:01.196
And I think you're the one
who needs protection,

38:02.113 --> 38:03.740
not me.

38:08.620 --> 38:09.662
[chuckles]

38:10.538 --> 38:11.664
I know.

38:12.207 --> 38:13.208
What?

38:14.375 --> 38:15.960
How are you so calm?

38:16.044 --> 38:18.087
-Because I'm relieved.
-About what?

38:18.171 --> 38:20.924
I would be terrified right now
if you were the target.

38:22.634 --> 38:23.718
But if I'm the target…

38:25.887 --> 38:26.888
I thank the heavens.

38:29.516 --> 38:31.142
[♪ gentle music playing]

38:38.358 --> 38:39.567
-[grunts]
-Ah!

38:42.362 --> 38:43.613
Have you lost your mind?

38:43.696 --> 38:46.574
And if you make me a widow? What then?

38:46.658 --> 38:48.827
Why are you thanking the heavens?

38:48.910 --> 38:51.871
You expect me to live
in the palace alone? Without you?

38:51.955 --> 38:52.956
Stop it already.

38:57.126 --> 38:59.295
If something terrible happens to you…

39:04.551 --> 39:06.010
I can't even get divorced.

39:11.015 --> 39:12.225
[laughs]

39:13.309 --> 39:14.310
You think this is funny?

39:14.394 --> 39:16.563
You have a dramatic way
of expressing concern.

39:23.361 --> 39:24.445
Just lie down.

39:31.202 --> 39:32.287
You're a royal now.

39:33.413 --> 39:34.706
So what?

39:35.373 --> 39:37.417
Do I have to keep quiet
even if I'm being targeted?

39:40.086 --> 39:42.046
You must exercise your royal powers.

39:44.215 --> 39:45.216
Which are?

39:47.260 --> 39:48.678
INVITATION TO ROYAL ACADEMY
80TH ANNIVERSARY

39:48.761 --> 39:49.762
SCHEDULE OF PUBLIC EVENTS

39:52.891 --> 39:55.184
-[Hyejeong] Fashion Week.
-[Hyeon] Oh, Fashion Week?

39:55.268 --> 39:58.229
[I-AN] In grand assemblies,
you shall embody the pride of the realm.

40:03.484 --> 40:04.485
[Hyeon] Right.

40:08.239 --> 40:09.407
[I-AN] And in places of honor,

40:10.241 --> 40:11.618
you shall embody its glory…

40:13.578 --> 40:14.787
to be loved?

40:16.039 --> 40:17.040
Hmm?

40:17.123 --> 40:20.376
Who would dare harm a person who is
the nation's pride and glory?
STYLE
::cue()

40:22.795 --> 40:25.757
Does that belief embolden you
to be so reckless?

40:25.840 --> 40:27.926
Because you are
"the nation's pride and glory"?

40:28.885 --> 40:29.886
[scoffs]

40:30.929 --> 40:32.513
I was never reckless.

40:32.597 --> 40:33.598
I just sometimes

40:34.557 --> 40:35.600
do what I want to do.

40:38.102 --> 40:39.187
[gasps] Oh.

40:39.270 --> 40:41.022
-I don't know what to do.
-About what?

40:41.105 --> 40:42.190
Earlier, the Queen Mother

40:42.690 --> 40:44.901
said she'd perform
my public duties on my behalf.

40:45.485 --> 40:46.945
[chuckles] Oh, that?

40:47.570 --> 40:48.821
It's fine.

40:51.532 --> 40:52.533
I denied her request.

41:00.208 --> 41:02.126
There is to be no change to my schedule?

41:02.210 --> 41:03.544
His Royal Highness

41:04.295 --> 41:06.923
stated that all public duties
will be duly fulfilled,

41:08.216 --> 41:10.593
and that Your Majesty does not need

41:10.677 --> 41:11.761
to worry herself.

41:11.844 --> 41:12.845
[scoffs]

41:15.264 --> 41:17.850
It appears the Grand Prince refuses
to exercise any caution.

41:22.689 --> 41:25.149
[court lady] Your Majesty,
Lord INPYEONG has arrived.

41:26.943 --> 41:29.529
[♪ tense music playing]

41:33.574 --> 41:34.701
Show him in.

41:35.868 --> 41:37.537
[sighs]

41:39.580 --> 41:40.790
[sighs]

41:44.711 --> 41:48.006
You should refrain from visiting
the palace for the time being.

41:54.595 --> 41:57.849
I fear it may give rise
to unnecessary misunderstanding.

42:02.562 --> 42:03.646
Your Majesty

42:04.313 --> 42:06.274
would do well to exercise some caution.

42:08.317 --> 42:09.652
Do you care to elaborate?

42:11.195 --> 42:13.281
I meant nothing by it.

42:13.781 --> 42:14.782
I…

42:16.659 --> 42:18.411
only fear it may give rise

42:19.454 --> 42:21.080
to unnecessary misunderstanding.

42:38.431 --> 42:40.141
[music fades]

42:40.224 --> 42:41.225
[door closes]

42:43.895 --> 42:44.896
Sir.

42:53.112 --> 42:56.365
They discovered traces of digoxin
in a goblet used in the wedding rites.

42:58.743 --> 42:59.911
FORENSIC EXAMINATION REPORT

42:59.994 --> 43:01.829
PHOTO 1: GOBLET CONTAINING
TRACES OF DIGOXIN

43:01.913 --> 43:03.122
[Huiju] They were switched then.

43:03.748 --> 43:04.957
Our goblets.

43:06.375 --> 43:07.960
The medication he usually takes…

43:09.128 --> 43:10.421
Did you check those?

43:11.756 --> 43:13.883
What are you doing? Calm down!

43:13.966 --> 43:15.593
He's in danger right now!

43:16.886 --> 43:18.429
-[knocks on door]
-[door opens]

43:20.515 --> 43:22.433
[assistant]
Sir, Ms. Lee Areum has arrived.

43:41.619 --> 43:43.955
[Huiju] What? You're really that swamped?

43:45.123 --> 43:47.250
There you go with that nagging again.

43:48.209 --> 43:50.628
I swear I'm perfectly fine.

43:50.711 --> 43:52.088
Stop worrying for no reason.

43:56.509 --> 43:57.552
[sighs]

43:57.635 --> 44:00.263
[♪ pop music playing]

44:01.097 --> 44:02.098
[sighs]

44:04.142 --> 44:05.017
Oh…

44:05.101 --> 44:06.853
-[Hyejeong] Hello? Ms. Seong?
-Hey. I'm here.

44:07.854 --> 44:09.021
Yeah.

44:09.689 --> 44:10.898
Are you okay?

44:10.982 --> 44:12.900
Yeah, so nice. I mean, it's fine.

44:13.776 --> 44:14.819
See you tomorrow.

44:19.282 --> 44:21.200
It's our first night as a married couple.

44:30.835 --> 44:31.919
Are you ready?

44:46.017 --> 44:48.227
[machine beeping]
STYLE
::cue()

44:52.940 --> 44:54.066
[Hyeon] No way.

44:54.150 --> 44:57.278
I'm sure no one knows their way
around the palace better than me.

44:58.154 --> 45:00.656
That only shows you the main pathways.

45:00.740 --> 45:02.366
If you want to follow that,

45:02.450 --> 45:04.493
you should be prepared
to walk 12,000 steps.

45:04.994 --> 45:05.995
Are you sure?

45:06.078 --> 45:07.413
You should trust me.

45:07.496 --> 45:08.789
If you go this way,

45:08.873 --> 45:10.541
you'll be in your room in ten minutes.

45:15.296 --> 45:17.798
When did you start working at the palace?

45:19.133 --> 45:20.218
What?

45:20.301 --> 45:23.012
I mean, you're still pretty young.

45:23.512 --> 45:25.640
But you know everything,
like you were born here.

45:25.723 --> 45:27.183
From the staff to the pathways.

45:28.643 --> 45:32.230
I'm not exactly sure.
I think I was five or six?

45:33.064 --> 45:34.065
What?

45:34.565 --> 45:35.900
I'm an orphan, you see.

45:37.193 --> 45:39.737
I heard I was abandoned
in front of the private residence.

45:41.739 --> 45:44.242
[whimpers] Sorry.

45:45.076 --> 45:46.077
Pardon?

45:46.160 --> 45:49.330
I shouldn't have asked. Right?

45:49.914 --> 45:51.707
Oh! No, it's perfectly fine.

45:51.791 --> 45:53.084
You see,

45:53.626 --> 45:57.004
I'm really grateful to my parents.

45:57.588 --> 46:00.508
I grew up surrounded by love
at the private residence.

46:00.591 --> 46:03.135
Of all places, I just happened
to be abandoned right in front

46:03.219 --> 46:04.971
of the Grand Prince's house.

46:05.721 --> 46:08.724
You could say
I'm sort of a "lucky guy." [laughs]

46:08.808 --> 46:10.810
[♪ gentle music playing]

46:19.694 --> 46:21.988
[heartbeat thumping]

46:28.369 --> 46:31.038
What are you doing?
We need to make it in 10 minutes.

46:31.122 --> 46:32.123
Right.

46:34.417 --> 46:35.418
What's wrong with you?

46:46.679 --> 46:48.514
[machine beeping]

46:48.597 --> 46:49.598
[sighs]

46:52.601 --> 46:53.811
[clears throat]

46:56.522 --> 46:59.692
Will you not even consider the sofa?

46:59.775 --> 47:00.776
[I-AN] No.

47:01.444 --> 47:02.903
This is perfectly fine.

47:03.696 --> 47:05.406
The sofa would be perfectly fine too.

47:06.198 --> 47:07.408
Then you should go.

47:08.492 --> 47:09.785
That'd be perfect.

47:13.164 --> 47:14.373
I'm the patient here.

47:15.833 --> 47:17.376
[I-AN mumbles]

47:17.460 --> 47:18.461
[sighs]

47:25.092 --> 47:26.510
Seriously?

47:29.972 --> 47:31.265
Just sleep already.

47:31.349 --> 47:33.893
Want everyone to think
I was cast aside on our first night?

47:36.354 --> 47:38.689
[machine beeping]

47:46.947 --> 47:48.366
[sighs]

48:00.586 --> 48:02.254
Should we turn that off?

48:06.050 --> 48:07.051
Just leave it.

48:07.134 --> 48:08.344
[sighs]

48:09.345 --> 48:10.846
But it's so loud.

48:12.473 --> 48:14.225
It's proof you're alive.

48:16.185 --> 48:18.521
[♪ soft pop playing]

48:22.358 --> 48:23.359
I like the sound of it.

48:41.502 --> 48:42.837
I'm just reassuring you.

48:44.797 --> 48:46.298
I'm right here.

49:01.230 --> 49:02.648
[sighs]
STYLE
::cue()

49:45.399 --> 49:48.152
Both her blood pressure
and pulse are stable.

49:48.235 --> 49:49.278
[Lady Choi] Thank you.

49:50.446 --> 49:51.447
Ms. Do--

49:52.198 --> 49:53.199
Aide Do!

49:53.991 --> 49:55.034
[Hyeon] Yes?

50:00.164 --> 50:01.582
I didn't call for you.

50:01.665 --> 50:05.169
I know, but you should ask for me
for the time being.

50:05.252 --> 50:08.047
I will be the chief aide
of the Grand Princess for now.

50:08.130 --> 50:09.298
-Why?
-Mmm,

50:09.381 --> 50:11.550
because you'll need
an experienced aide

50:11.634 --> 50:14.345
well-versed in royal duties by your side

50:14.428 --> 50:16.055
to facilitate your swift transition.

50:16.138 --> 50:18.307
Th-Then what about my Ms. Do?

50:18.390 --> 50:19.558
Where is my Hyejeong?

50:20.434 --> 50:22.603
-What did you do with her?
-She's safe.

50:22.686 --> 50:23.854
Hyejeong!

50:23.938 --> 50:27.107
It's a Royal Academy event,
so security shouldn't be a major issue.

50:27.191 --> 50:30.027
It's a small-scale event
that will be held indoors.

50:30.110 --> 50:31.320
[I-AN clears throat]

50:33.614 --> 50:36.408
You should be familiar
with most of the guests.

50:36.492 --> 50:37.868
They're all former students.

50:51.215 --> 50:52.841
Anyone I should be mindful of?

50:53.592 --> 50:54.718
Prime Minister Min Jeongwoo.

50:54.802 --> 50:56.595
He is set to deliver the opening address.

50:56.679 --> 50:58.806
Your Royal Highness
will present the scholarship.

51:03.310 --> 51:04.311
[chuckles]

51:08.899 --> 51:11.902
There are a few protocols
you must follow during official duties.

51:11.986 --> 51:15.030
First, you must never walk
ahead of His Royal Highness.

51:15.114 --> 51:18.909
Hold on. This was something I mentioned
for the Inner Court Banquet as well.

51:19.451 --> 51:21.745
Court rank is very important
in official events.

51:21.829 --> 51:23.914
I understand.

51:24.582 --> 51:26.041
Yes. Thank you. [clears throat]

51:26.125 --> 51:29.003
You will sometimes come across
people who hand you flowers or letters.

51:29.086 --> 51:30.337
You should accept all of them.

51:30.421 --> 51:32.089
-All of them?
-Yes, all of them.

51:32.172 --> 51:34.466
And your photo could be taken at any time.

51:34.550 --> 51:36.010
So try not to appear

51:36.093 --> 51:38.470
expressionless or put on that face
you just gave me.

51:38.554 --> 51:40.306
There you go again.

51:40.389 --> 51:41.932
You cannot do that.

51:42.516 --> 51:46.437
Also, you must observe rank when offering
a handshake or initiating a conversation.

51:46.520 --> 51:49.440
His Royal Highness is first.
You come second.

51:49.523 --> 51:52.401
Does that mean no one can speak to me
if I don't speak to them first?

51:52.484 --> 51:53.569
Correct.

51:53.652 --> 51:55.529
And you can never show bare feet.

51:55.613 --> 51:58.574
If there are no slippers available,
please keep your shoes on.

51:58.657 --> 52:01.619
Crossing your legs while seated
is strictly forbidden,

52:01.702 --> 52:02.786
so please be careful.

52:02.870 --> 52:05.998
No peace signs or finger hearts
when being photographed.

52:06.081 --> 52:07.875
Cheek hearts? Definitely not.

52:08.375 --> 52:10.502
Then what exactly am I supposed to do?

52:10.586 --> 52:12.171
Something simple.

52:13.130 --> 52:14.715
Maybe a simple wave?

52:14.798 --> 52:15.883
[sighs]

52:17.384 --> 52:18.510
Ah…

52:19.803 --> 52:21.930
I should wear this one today.

52:22.014 --> 52:24.850
I should do my part to boost
our affiliate's revenue again.

52:25.684 --> 52:26.894
What do you think?

52:26.977 --> 52:28.145
[in English] Good choice.

52:29.813 --> 52:31.357
[in Korean] So pretty. Hmm.

52:33.525 --> 52:35.069
Ready to go?

52:35.152 --> 52:36.362
[chuckles]

52:37.655 --> 52:39.073
I will be after you change.

52:40.824 --> 52:42.993
Why? Do I look weird?

52:43.827 --> 52:46.497
It's our first official appearance
as a married couple.

52:46.580 --> 52:49.041
Our outfits should look coordinated.

52:49.124 --> 52:52.002
[clicks tongue]
Such a gloomy outfit. Right?

52:52.086 --> 52:53.545
-My thoughts exactly.
-Mmm.

52:55.255 --> 52:56.507
-Just look at it.
-[gasps]

52:56.590 --> 52:57.966
[in English] So shiny!

52:58.050 --> 52:59.134
Wow.

52:59.635 --> 53:01.679
[in Korean]
We must leave a record of this. Right?

53:01.762 --> 53:03.555
All right now. Here we go.

53:03.639 --> 53:04.973
Look right over here.

53:05.474 --> 53:07.226
-Let's try smiling.
-[giggling]

53:07.309 --> 53:08.769
Oh, my gosh.

53:08.852 --> 53:10.270
-Oh, my goodness.
-[Huiju] Shall we?

53:10.854 --> 53:12.147
Shall we take this to the hallway?

53:12.231 --> 53:14.233
Come on now. Here we go.

53:15.818 --> 53:17.319
Does it look gloomy?

53:17.403 --> 53:20.030
Absolutely not.
You look so cool right now.

53:20.114 --> 53:21.115
"Gloomy"?

53:21.198 --> 53:23.992
[scoffs] How could she say that
to the world's most handsome man?

53:29.665 --> 53:31.709
-Sir.
-I was actually just on my way out.

53:31.792 --> 53:33.210
You need to take a look at this.

53:44.179 --> 53:46.598
Criticism of the Crown
will be unavoidable.

53:46.682 --> 53:47.641
What do you think?

53:50.310 --> 53:51.478
[breathes shakily]
STYLE
::cue()

53:53.439 --> 53:55.983
[♪ upbeat music playing]

54:03.031 --> 54:06.201
[crowd cheering]

54:28.348 --> 54:29.725
Aren't we going inside?

54:30.768 --> 54:32.186
Enough of that. Take my arm.

54:33.312 --> 54:35.105
Why? I'm busy being loved.

54:35.189 --> 54:37.816
[chuckles] Go on without me.

54:45.032 --> 54:46.200
They look so affectionate.

54:46.700 --> 54:47.701
I know, right?

54:51.622 --> 54:52.623
[clears throat]

55:09.890 --> 55:12.351
[Hyeon] I made it so crystal clear

55:12.434 --> 55:15.020
that you can't do these finger hearts…
[laughs]

55:15.103 --> 55:16.438
Please stop that.

55:16.522 --> 55:18.065
Come on now.

55:18.148 --> 55:19.775
P-Please stop, Your Royal Highness.

55:20.567 --> 55:21.777
[Hyejeong] Yes, sure.

55:22.277 --> 55:23.320
Thank you.

55:23.403 --> 55:24.821
[call end tone]

55:24.905 --> 55:27.407
Your Royal Highness,
that was the prime minister's office.

55:27.491 --> 55:28.867
He's going to be a little late.

55:28.951 --> 55:30.285
-Really?
-Jeongwoo is?

55:30.953 --> 55:31.954
Can you…

55:32.663 --> 55:34.706
stop addressing him like that?

55:36.833 --> 55:38.627
I'm not supposed to call him by his name?

55:38.710 --> 55:42.005
-"Prime Minister Min."
-[Hyejeong] You should first review this.

55:42.589 --> 55:43.840
Why?

55:43.924 --> 55:45.467
They sent over the opening address.

55:45.968 --> 55:47.761
Since he is presenting the scholarships,

55:47.844 --> 55:50.597
wouldn't it be nice
if you delivered the opening address?

55:52.474 --> 55:55.894
[♪ gentle music playing]

55:55.978 --> 55:57.312
[chuckles]

55:58.814 --> 56:01.316
[cheering]

56:08.115 --> 56:10.158
Hello, I am Seong Huiju.

56:15.622 --> 56:17.374
Being back at my alma mater,

56:17.958 --> 56:20.252
I feel like I should be
introducing myself by saying,

56:20.335 --> 56:22.004
"I am Seong Huiju of Jujak House."

56:23.338 --> 56:26.133
Another part of me wants to celebrate
my success since graduating

56:27.217 --> 56:29.469
by presenting myself
as Seong Huiju, the Executive Director

56:30.053 --> 56:31.471
of Castle Group.

56:32.681 --> 56:36.310
However, I am sure
all of you would most like to hear,

56:38.145 --> 56:39.187
"Hello,

56:40.022 --> 56:41.690
I am Grand Princess Seong Huiju."

56:43.525 --> 56:44.651
Am I right?

56:44.735 --> 56:48.113
[crowd laughing]

56:50.782 --> 56:52.451
-[laughs]
-She's unbelievable.

56:54.578 --> 56:56.455
-She's so good, isn't she?
-[phone buzzing]

56:58.290 --> 56:59.499
[sighs]

57:00.334 --> 57:02.919
[♪ tense music playing]

57:16.808 --> 57:18.060
[Huiju] Eighty years ago,

57:18.644 --> 57:20.646
when the Royal Academy was founded,

57:20.729 --> 57:23.690
the Crown pursued but one ideal.

57:24.650 --> 57:27.736
Any who aspired to become something

57:28.654 --> 57:29.988
shall be allowed to do so,

57:30.614 --> 57:32.949
without regard to background

57:33.659 --> 57:34.951
or gender.

57:35.035 --> 57:38.538
I, too, was a beneficiary of that mission,

57:39.581 --> 57:40.749
and as you can see,

57:41.333 --> 57:45.212
I managed to make
all my aspirations a reality.

57:45.295 --> 57:47.756
[crowd laughing]

57:47.839 --> 57:48.882
Your Royal Highness.

57:54.805 --> 57:57.891
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

57:57.974 --> 58:00.894
A PERSON OF VIRTUE
TAKES RIGHTEOUSNESS…

58:00.977 --> 58:02.396
TAKEN AS FOUNDATION

58:07.275 --> 58:08.694
There is an emergency, Your Majesty.

58:09.945 --> 58:11.405
What is it?

58:11.488 --> 58:14.074
If there is something that you want,

58:15.075 --> 58:16.076
do not hesitate…

58:16.159 --> 58:18.286
-[phones buzzing]
-…and claim it for yourself.

58:20.747 --> 58:23.166
As your senior alum and patron,

58:24.042 --> 58:26.378
with ironclad resolve…

58:27.087 --> 58:29.214
-[crowd murmuring]
-[clears throat]

58:33.510 --> 58:35.595
With ironclad resolve…

58:36.596 --> 58:38.598
-[door opens]
-[reporters clamoring]

58:40.475 --> 58:42.978
[reporter 1] Your Royal Highness!

58:43.061 --> 58:45.731
Do you have anything to say for yourself?

58:45.814 --> 58:47.441
[reporter 2] Did you deceive the people?

58:47.524 --> 58:50.068
[reporter 3] There was a confidentiality
clause. What are you hiding?
STYLE
::cue()

58:51.403 --> 58:53.864
EXCLUSIVE: THE ROYAL COUPLE'S
MARRIAGE CONTRACT LEAKED

58:53.947 --> 58:57.200
[♪ tense music playing]

58:57.284 --> 58:59.536
[reporter 4] Is it true that that
the marriage is contractual?

58:59.619 --> 59:02.164
[reporter 5] Is it true
you plan to divorce in three years?

59:02.247 --> 59:03.540
Please respond!

59:10.422 --> 59:11.965
Was there consent from the royal family?

59:12.048 --> 59:14.259
What has Castle Group promised the Crown?

59:24.770 --> 59:27.397
[clamoring fades]

59:38.742 --> 59:40.911
[clamoring]

59:44.164 --> 59:45.415
What are you doing?

59:47.667 --> 59:48.668
Keep your eyes on me.

59:48.752 --> 59:49.669
[clamoring fades]

59:49.753 --> 59:53.089
[♪ soft pop playing]

01:00:07.479 --> 01:00:09.481
[reporters clamoring]

01:00:11.691 --> 01:00:13.360
[clamoring fades]

01:00:22.953 --> 01:00:25.872
PERFECT CROWN

01:01:01.908 --> 01:01:04.286
[reporter] Is it true that
the marriage is contractual?

01:01:04.369 --> 01:01:05.996
[Hyeon] This is about to blow up
in our face.

01:01:06.079 --> 01:01:09.583
[Yun] You thought you could protect
yourself with that measly contract?

01:01:10.166 --> 01:01:12.377
I shall set the record straight myself.

01:01:12.460 --> 01:01:14.379
Can Your Majesty prove it?

01:01:14.462 --> 01:01:16.464
Do you think I'm oblivious
to your scheming?

01:01:16.548 --> 01:01:17.549
Your Royal Highness!

01:01:18.550 --> 01:01:19.968
[Jeongwoo] You said it was all for show.

01:01:20.051 --> 01:01:21.428
You and the Grand Prince.

01:01:22.345 --> 01:01:23.513
[Huiju] I like him.

01:01:24.014 --> 01:01:25.098
A lot.

01:01:26.266 --> 01:01:27.183
HUIJU

01:01:27.267 --> 01:01:29.019
[Jeongwoo]
His Royal Highness remains unaware.

01:01:29.102 --> 01:01:30.353
[Yun] How does it feel?

01:01:30.437 --> 01:01:31.855
[Huiju] What do I have to do?

01:01:33.523 --> 01:01:34.524
[I-AN] Are you scared?

01:01:35.442 --> 01:01:37.652
[Huiju] I'm scared I might end up

01:01:37.736 --> 01:01:38.778
ruining you.

01:01:44.826 --> 01:01:49.039
EPILOGUE

01:01:49.122 --> 01:01:51.833
[machine beeping]

01:01:52.500 --> 01:01:54.628
[♪ uplifting music playing]

01:01:59.716 --> 01:02:02.510
Your Royal Highness,
it is Court Lady Choi.

01:02:02.594 --> 01:02:04.137
[Huiju mumbles]

01:02:04.220 --> 01:02:05.680
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness.

01:02:06.348 --> 01:02:07.766
[groans]

01:02:08.850 --> 01:02:10.143
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness!

01:02:19.486 --> 01:02:21.154
Are you awake?

01:02:23.406 --> 01:02:24.741
[sighs]

01:02:24.824 --> 01:02:26.618
-Should I just go in there?
-[phone buzzes]

01:02:26.701 --> 01:02:27.994
Would that be okay?

01:02:28.495 --> 01:02:29.871
IF YOU WAKE UP
THE GRAND PRINCESS…

01:02:29.955 --> 01:02:31.039
-Your Royal High--
-Stop.

01:02:32.624 --> 01:02:34.334
He says to keep it down.

01:02:35.126 --> 01:02:36.211
Pardon me?

01:02:36.294 --> 01:02:38.380
He says if we wake
the Grand Princess… [sucks teeth]

01:02:38.463 --> 01:02:39.756
…there will be hell to pay.

01:02:40.799 --> 01:02:41.841
[chuckles]

01:02:44.135 --> 01:02:46.429
-Should we go get some breakfast?
-Shall we?

01:02:47.973 --> 01:02:49.015
What are you craving?

01:02:49.099 --> 01:02:51.518
There's a place with amazing pajeon
right by here.

01:03:31.891 --> 01:03:33.893
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:03:45.196 --> 01:03:48.908
PERFECT CROWN
